{"body":"[{\"data\":1,\"prerenderedAt\":108},[\"ShallowReactive\",2],{\"navigation\":3,\"\\u002Fblog\\u002Fbuilding-my-personal-site-with-nuxt\":22,\"\\u002Fblog\\u002Fbuilding-my-personal-site-with-nuxt-surround\":104},[4],{\"title\":5,\"path\":6,\"stem\":7,\"children\":8,\"page\":21},\"Blog\",\"\\u002Fblog\",\"blog\",[9,13,17],{\"title\":10,\"path\":11,\"stem\":12},\"用 Nuxt 初始化个人简历与技术博客\",\"\\u002Fblog\\u002Fbuilding-my-personal-site-with-nuxt\",\"blog\\u002Fbuilding-my-personal-site-with-nuxt\",{\"title\":14,\"path\":15,\"stem\":16},\"前端工程化笔记：从可运行到可维护\",\"\\u002Fblog\\u002Ffrontend-engineering-notes\",\"blog\\u002Ffrontend-engineering-notes\",{\"title\":18,\"path\":19,\"stem\":20},\"项目复盘模板：把经历写成作品\",\"\\u002Fblog\\u002Fproject-review-template\",\"blog\\u002Fproject-review-template\",false,{\"id\":23,\"title\":10,\"author\":24,\"body\":29,\"date\":95,\"description\":96,\"extension\":97,\"image\":98,\"meta\":99,\"minRead\":100,\"navigation\":101,\"path\":11,\"seo\":102,\"stem\":12,\"__hash__\":103},\"blog\\u002Fblog\\u002Fbuilding-my-personal-site-with-nuxt.md\",{\"name\":25,\"description\":26,\"avatar\":27},\"你的名字\",\"前端 \\u002F 全栈开发者\",{\"src\":28,\"alt\":25},\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fimages.unsplash.com\\u002Fphoto-1701615004837-40d8573b6652?q=80&w=1480&auto=format&fit=crop\",{\"type\":30,\"value\":31,\"toc\":88},\"minimark\",[32,36,41,44,47,82,85],[33,34,35],\"p\",{},\"这个站点使用 Nuxt、Nuxt UI 和 Nuxt Content 构建。它不是一个单纯的静态简历，而是一个可以持续更新的个人内容系统：简历负责说明“我是谁”，项目页负责说明“我做过什么”，博客负责沉淀“我如何思考和解决问题”。\",[37,38,40],\"h2\",{\"id\":39},\"为什么选择-nuxt\",\"为什么选择 Nuxt\",[33,42,43],{},\"Nuxt 对内容型站点很友好，路由、SEO、图片、组件系统和构建流程都比较完整。配合 Nuxt Content，可以直接用 Markdown 管理文章，用 YAML 管理首页、项目和简历信息。\",[37,45,46],{\"id\":46},\"当前结构\",[48,49,50,58,64,70,76],\"ul\",{},[51,52,53,57],\"li\",{},[54,55,56],\"code\",{},\"content\\u002Findex.yml\",\"：首页文案、工作经历和 FAQ\",[51,59,60,63],{},[54,61,62],{},\"content\\u002Fabout.yml\",\"：在线简历正文\",[51,65,66,69],{},[54,67,68],{},\"content\\u002Fprojects\\u002F*.yml\",\"：项目作品\",[51